	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />True, but as a rule, division by a variable is hard to pipeline in modern CPU hardware. So any inner loop with a division in it should be one of the first targets of your profiling instrumentation.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
